<h1>Why Hitmunk Exists</h1>
<p class='lead'>Hitmunk's mission is to bring healthcare practitioners,
technologists, and enthusiasts together to share and grow the industry's
knowledge base. By doing so, we hope to connect the people who have knowledge
to the people who need it, leading to the creation of intelligent solutions and
answers for better quality of life.
</p>
<br>
<p>
  The heart and soul of Hitmunk is discussion- whether that be around breaking
  industry news or a question about a particular topic. Discussion can be sparked
  by anyone- patients, doctors, nurses, CEOs, software developers, social workers,
  CMIOs, and everyone in between. Everyone is invited to give their meaningful
  perspective with the goal of creating a well-rounded, definitive threads of
  useful information.
</p>
